#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Phone" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
This field is the primary phone number for this patron.  It may be able to receive texts
but it should always be able to take phone calls.
<p>
It is in the form:
<div class=field_format>(nnn)nnn-nnnn</div>

<p>Note that if you just type in the digits, it will rewrite it to that form.

